Package org.bongz.constants

Class FrameworkConstants

java.lang.Object
org.bongz.constants.FrameworkConstants
public final class FrameworkConstants extends Object
Framework Constants holds all the constant values used within the framework. If some value needs to be changed or modified often, then it should be stored in the property files Mar 7, 2022
